Help me out! Hold him!

87
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,446
We're going to the sink!

88
00:06:02,644 --> 00:06:04,336
l got to get up! l got to get up!

89
00:06:04,532 --> 00:06:05,939
-Cool it!
-Put water on it!

90
00:06:06,133 --> 00:06:07,061
More water!

91
00:06:07,253 --> 00:06:09,227
