01:46:07,821 --> 01:46:11,617
You shouldn't join any organization
unless you know what it's about.

1518
01:46:18,028 --> 01:46:19,272
Thank you.

1519
01:46:20,876 --> 01:46:23,113
You shouldn't give up
so easily either.

1520
01:46:25,068 --> 01:46:28,200
We could use more young warriors
like yourself.

1521
01:46:28,427 --> 01:46:30,761
Come on by the temple
next Wednesday, 8:00.

1522
01:46:30,987 --> 01:46:32,133
8:00 sharp.

1523
01:46:32,331 --> 01:46:34,086
Yes, sir. 8:00 sharp.

1524
01:46:34,283 --> 01:46:37,447
Thank you, Mr. X. And l won't
make you out a liar either.

1525
01:46:37,644 --> 01:46:38,822
l don't think you will.

1526
01:46:51,467 --> 01:46:52,841
Tonight, l shall...

1527
01:46:53,321 --> 01:46:57,119
...introduce you
as my national minister.

1528
01:46:58,314 --> 01:47:00,681
lt will be a difficult task.

1529
01:47:01,066 --> 01:47:02,592
Your assignment...

1530
01:47:03,402 --> 01:47:05,955
...is to build temples
all over this nation.

1531
01:47:07,016 --> 01:47:09,025
More work than you've ever done.

1532
01:47:09,227 --> 01:47:10,241
Yes, sir.

1533
01:47:10,443 --> 01:47:12,384
You will be in the public eye.

1534
01:47:12,586 --> 01:47:15,105
Beware of them cameras.

1535
01:47:17,385 --> 01:47:18,662
Them cameras are...

1536
01:47:19,402 --> 01:47:21,539
...bad as any narcotic.

1537
01:47:24,360 --> 01:47:26,946
White devil will be watching
your every step.

1538
01:47:27,561 --> 01:47:29,928
And your own brothers will be...

1539
01:47:30,984 --> 01:47:32,358
...jealous...

1540
01:47:33,000 --> 01:47:34,658
...hostile.

1541
01:47:35,560 --> 01:47:36,803
Go slowly.

1542
01:47:37,096 --> 01:47:38,176
Yes, sir.

1543
01:47:39,465 --> 01:47:40,839
Here's a glass.

1544
01:47:47,367 --> 01:47:49,256
lt's dirty water.

1545
01:47:49,449 --> 01:47:50,496
Foul.

1546
01:47:52,232 --> 01:47:54,566
lf you offer this to the people...

1547
01:47:54,759 --> 01:47:56,515
...they have no choice.

1548
01:47:56,935 --> 01:47:58,341
They'll drink from it...

1549
01:47:59,270 --> 01:48:00,765
...if they're thirsty.

1550
01:48:01,672 --> 01:48:03,427
But if you offer them...

1551
01:48:04,199 --> 01:48:05,824
...this glass...

1552
01:48:08,518 --> 01:48:11,617
...and let them make
their own decision...

1553
01:48:12,423 --> 01:48:15,554
...they will choose the pure vessel.

1554
01:48:17,478 --> 01:48:18,886
lslam is...

1555
01:48:19,302 --> 01:48:21,474
...the only religion...

1556
01:48:22,599 --> 01:48:25,598
...that addresses
the needs and the problems...

1557
01:48:25,797 --> 01:48:29,856
...of the so-called Negro in America.
Especially in the slums...

1558
01:48:30,054 --> 01:48:31,397
...in the ghettos.

1559
01:48:32,070 --> 01:48:35,998
lslam is the only way out
for drugs and crime...

1560
01:48:36,197 --> 01:48:38,302
...and unemployment, prostitution...

1561
01:48:38,502 --> 01:48:40,061
...alcohol...

1562
01:48:40,262 --> 01:48:41,603
...gambling...

1563
01:48:41,797 --> 01:48:43,969
...and adultery, fornication.

1564
01:48:45,221 --> 01:48:46,269
This sweet...

1565
01:48:46,500 --> 01:48:50,657
...gentle man, at whose feet I kneeled,
gave me the truth from his own mouth.

1566
01:48:50,917 --> 01:48:52,062
Present the pure vessel.

1567
01:48:52,260 --> 01:48:56,416
I adored him in the sense of
the Latin root of the word adorare...

1568
01:48:56,613 --> 01:48:58,586
...which means to worship and to fear.

1569
01:48:59,108 --> 01:49:00,864
He was the first man I ever feared.

1570
01:49:01,060 --> 01:49:03,581
I don't mean fear
such as one has of a gun...

1571
01:49:03,780 --> 01:49:07,424
...but the fear one has
of the power of the sun.

1572
01:49:07,715 --> 01:49:10,879
I pledged myself to him,
even if it cost me my life.

1573
01:49:14,213 --> 01:49:15,903
-Hello?
-Hello, Betty?

1574
01:49:16,196 --> 01:49:17,373
Yeah, this is Malcolm.

1575
01:49:17,765 --> 01:49:20,317
-l know.
-Right, I'm here in Detroit.

1576
01:49:24,260 --> 01:49:26,299
-Will you marry me?
-Yes.

1577
01:49:26,692 --> 01:49:28,066
You heard what I said, right?

1578
01:49:28,260 --> 01:49:30,561
-Did you hear my answer?
-Yes, l think so.

1579
01:49:32,994 --> 01:49:35,548
-Are you eating?
-l've been eating.

1580
01:49:35,779 --> 01:49:36,793
Good.

1581
01:49:37,508 --> 01:49:38,816
I love you, Betty.

1582
01:49:41,313 --> 01:49:43,223
I love you back.

1583
01:49:53,090 --> 01:49:54,431
lt's not gonna be easy.

1584
01:49:54,627 --> 01:49:56,088
No choice.

1585
01:49:56,577 --> 01:49:58,104
l'll be away a lot.

1586
01:49:58,913 --> 01:50:00,124
l know.

1587
01:50:02,817 --> 01:50:04,706
ln fact, l'm leaving in the morning.

1588
01:50:04,899 --> 01:50:06,328
Hush, now.

1589
01:50:07,138 --> 01:50:09,210
Pittsburgh, Philadelphia...

1590
01:50:10,818 --> 01:50:14,428
...Trenton, Newark, up through number 7
all the way up to Boston.

1591
01:50:20,928 --> 01:50:22,554
You're with me...

1592
01:50:23,808 --> 01:50:25,697
...even when you're away.

1593
01:50:41,537 --> 01:50:43,772
l've never told you this...

1594
01:50:46,273 --> 01:50:48,989
...but the very first time
l ever saw you...

1595
01:50:50,016 --> 01:50:52,022
...standing up on the podium...

1596
01:50:54,526 --> 01:50:56,667
...you were cleaning your glasses...

1597
01:50:59,232 --> 01:51:01,848
...and l felt so sorry for you.

1598
01:51:02,751 --> 01:51:04,027
Sorry for me?

1599
01:51:04,479 --> 01:51:05,306
Why?

1600
01:51:05,503 --> 01:51:09,944
Because no one as young as you
should be so serious.

1601
01:51:12,799 --> 01:51:14,741
But l don't think that anymore.

1602
01:51:15,359 --> 01:51:16,667
What do you think?

1603
01:51:19,551 --> 01:51:22,333
l want to have
a lot of babies with you.

1604
01:51:25,950 --> 01:51:27,377
Dear heart.

1605
01:51:29,854 --> 01:51:31,228
l love you.

1606
01:51:33,375 --> 01:51:36,156
We're waiting on you folks.
Trying to starve us?

1607
01:51:39,454 --> 01:51:41,493
Brother Malcolm, Sister Betty...

1608
01:51:41,693 --> 01:51:46,035
...we pray that Allah blesses you
with a happy and fruitful marriage.

1609
01:51:48,925 --> 01:51:51,162
Congratulations, Brother Minister.

1610
01:51:53,373 --> 01:51:55,544
Check them out. Front page!

1611
01:51:59,868 --> 01:52:04,538
l must emphasize at the start that
Elijah Muhammad is not a politician.

1612
01:52:05,149 --> 01:52:09,786
So l'm not here this afternoon
as a Republican nor as a Democrat.

1613
01:52:11,293 --> 01:52:13,845
Not as a Mason nor as an Elk.

1614
01:52:15,132 --> 01:52:17,749
Not as a Protestant nor a Catholic.

1615
01:52:17,947 --> 01:52:20,533
Not as a Christian nor a Jew.

1616
01:52:20,731 --> 01:52:22,968
Not as a Baptist nor a Methodist.

1617
01:52:23,164 --> 01:52:25,464
ln fact, not even as an American.

1618
01:52:26,171 --> 01:52:28,178
Because if l was an American...

1619
01:52:28,410 --> 01:52:31,891
...the problem that confronts our people
today wouldn't even exist.

1620
01:52:35,163 --> 01:52:38,458
So l have to stand here today
as what l was when l was born...

1621
01:52:38,747 --> 01:52:40,241
...a black man.

1622
01:52:44,666 --> 01:52:49,172
Before there was any such thing as a
Republican or a Democrat, we were black.

1623
01:52:49,370 --> 01:52:53,015
Before there was any such thing
as a Mason or an Elk, we were black.

1624
01:52:53,210 --> 01:52:57,269
Before there was any such thing as a Jew
or a Christian, we were black people.

1625
01:52:57,466 --> 01:53:01,656
ln fact, before there was any such place
as America, we were black.

1626
01:53:01,914 --> 01:53:05,263
And after America has long passed
from the scene...

1627
01:53:05,465 --> 01:53:07,832
...there will still be black people.

1628
01:53:08,824 --> 01:53:11,377
l'm gonna tell you like it really is!

1629
01:53:12,090 --> 01:53:16,694
Every election year, these politicians
are sent up here to pacify us.

1630
01:53:16,890 --> 01:53:19,572
They're sent here and set up here
by the white man.

1631
01:53:19,768 --> 01:53:21,013
This is what they do.

1632
01:53:21,209 --> 01:53:23,990
They send drugs in Harlem down here
to pacify us!

1633
01:53:24,185 --> 01:53:26,770
They send alcohol down here
to pacify us!

1634
01:53:26,969 --> 01:53:29,816
They send prostitution down here
to pacify us!

1635
01:53:30,009 --> 01:53:33,271
You can't get drugs in Harlem
without the white man's permission.

1636
01:53:33,464 --> 01:53:36,628
You can't get prostitution in Harlem
without the white man's permission.

1637
01:53:36,825 --> 01:53:39,857
You can't get gambling in Harlem
without the white man's permission.

1638
01:53:40,056 --> 01:53:42,772
Every time you break the seal
on that liquor bottle...

1639
01:53:42,967 --> 01:53:45,424
...that's a government seal
you're breaking.

1640
01:53:45,623 --> 01:53:49,333
l say, and l say it again,
you been had.

1641
01:53:49,527 --> 01:53:50,989
You been took.

1642
01:53:51,192 --> 01:53:52,718
You been hoodwinked.

1643
01:53:53,046 --> 01:53:55,535
Bamboozled. Led astray.

1644
01:53:55,768 --> 01:53:58,156
Run amuck. This is what he does.

1645
01:53:58,423 --> 01:54:01,008
You know, some people
call this hate-teaching.

1646
01:54:01,334 --> 01:54:03,221
This isn't hate-teaching.

1647
01:54:03,414 --> 01:54:04,975
This is love-teaching.

1648
01:54:05,559 --> 01:54:07,979
l wouldn't tell you this
if l didn't love you.

1649
